ng-none text-white\">Get in touch with <br/><span class=\"text-[#1AAD94]\">our specialists.</span></h1><p class=\"mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg text-white/70\">Have questions about our training programs, job placements, or consulting services? We're here to help you navigate your maritime career.</p></div></section><section class=\"py-24 container mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-12\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-8\"><div class=\"rounded-[32px] bg-white border border-[#E0E0E0] p-8 md:p-12 shadow-sm\"><div class=\"grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3 mb-12\"><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-[#F9FAFB] border border-[#E0E0E0] p-5 transition-all hover:border-[#1AAD94]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-white flex items-center justify-center text-[#1AAD94] shadow-sm\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:help-circle\" class=\"text-xl\"></iconify-icon></div><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:arrow-up-right\" class=\"text-gray-300\"></iconify-icon></div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-[#073057] mb-1\">General</h4><p class=\"text-xs text-[#6B7280]\">Corporate inquiries</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-[#F9FAFB] border border-[#E0E0E0] p-5 transition-all hover:border-[#1AAD94]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-white flex items-center justify-center text-[#1AAD94] shadow-sm\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:graduation-cap\" class=\"text-xl\"></iconify-icon></div><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:arrow-up-right\" class=\"text-gray-300\"></iconify-icon></div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-[#073057] mb-1\">Training</h4><p class=\"text-xs text-[#6B7280]\">Skill certifications</p></div><div class=\"rounded-2xl bg-[#F9FAFB] border border-[#E0E0E0] p-5 transition-all hover:border-[#1AAD94]\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-3\"><div class=\"h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-white flex items-center justify-center text-[#1AAD94] shadow-sm\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:users\" class=\"text-xl\"></iconify-icon></div><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:arrow-up-right\" class=\"text-gray-300\"></iconify-icon></div><h4 class=\"text-sm font-bold text-[#073057] mb-1\">Partners</h4><p class=\"text-xs text-[#6B7280]\">Strategic alliances</p></div></div><div class=\"mb-10\"><h2 class=\"text-[32px] font-extrabold text-[#073057] mb-4\">Send a Message</h2><p class=\"text-[#6B7280]\">Fill out the form below and a member of our team will reach out within 24 hours.</p></div><form class=\"grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"space-y-2\"><label class=\"text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#073057]/60\">Full Name</label><input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"John Doe\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-[#E0E0E0] bg-[#F9FAFB] px-5 py-4 focus:border-[#1AAD94] focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#1AAD94] transition-all\"></div><div class=\"space-y-2\"><label class=\"text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#073057]/60\">Email Address</label><input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"john@company.com\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-[#E0E0E0] bg-[#F9FAFB] px-5 py-4 focus:border-[#1AAD94] focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#1AAD94] transition-all\"></div><div class=\"space-y-2 md:col-span-2\"><label class=\"text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#073057]/60\">Subject</label><select class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-[#E0E0E0] bg-[#F9FAFB] px-5 py-4 focus:border-[#1AAD94] focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#1AAD94] transition-all\"><option>General Inquiry</option><option>Training & Certification</option><option>Job Placement Services</option><option>Partnership Proposal</option></select></div><div class=\"space-y-2 md:col-span-2\"><label class=\"text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#073057]/60\">Message</label><textarea rows=\"5\" placeholder=\"How can we help you?\" class=\"w-full rounded-xl border border-[#E0E0E0] bg-[#F9FAFB] px-5 py-4 focus:border-[#1AAD94] focus:outline-none focus:ring-1 focus:ring-[#1AAD94] transition-all\"></textarea></div><div class=\"md:col-span-2 pt-4 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4\"><button type=\"submit\" id=\"contact-form-submit\" class=\"px-8 py-4 bg-[#073057] text-white rounded-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm hover:brightness-110 transition-all shadow-lg\">Submit Inquiry</button><a href=\"#register\" id=\"contact-form-pathway\" class=\"px-8 py-4 border-2 border-[#E0E0E0] text-[#073057] rounded-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-sm hover:border-[#1AAD94] hover:text-[#1AAD94] transition-all flex items-center justify-center\">Start Your Pathway</a></div></form></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-4 space-y-8\"><div class=\"rounded-[32px] bg-white border border-[#E0E0E0] p-8 shadow-sm\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-extrabold text-[#073057] mb-4\">Best way to reach JCL</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-[#6B7280] mb-8\">Whether you're an individual looking to level up or an organization looking to build a pipeline, we have specialists dedicated to each sector.</p><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-[#1AAD94]/10 text-[#1AAD94]\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:mail\" class=\"text-xl\"></iconify-icon></div><div><h5 class=\"text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#073057]/60 mb-1\">Email Us</h5><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-[#073057]\">info@joseoceanjobs.com</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-[#1AAD94]/10 text-[#1AAD94]\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:phone-call\" class=\"text-xl\"></iconify-icon></div><div><h5 class=\"text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#073057]/60 mb-1\">Phone Support</h5><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-[#073057]\">+233 (0) 555-123-456</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\"><div class=\"flex h-10 w-10 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-[#1AAD94]/10 text-[#1AAD94]\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:map-pin\" class=\"text-xl\"></iconify-icon></div><div><h5 class=\"text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#073057]/60 mb-1\">Global Office</h5><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-[#073057]\">Accra, Ghana ΓÇó Maritime Sector</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"rounded-[32px] bg-[#073057] text-white overflow-hidden shadow-xl relative\"><img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1544620347-c4fd4a3d5957?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=600\" alt=\"Officer\" class=\"h-48 w-full object-cover opacity-60\"><div class=\"p-8\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white/10 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#7DE1D1] mb-6\"><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:compass\" class=\"text-sm\"></iconify-icon><span>Next Steps</span></div><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-extrabold mb-4\">Prefer a self-service route?</h3><p class=\"text-sm text-white/70 leading-relaxed mb-8\">Quickly find what you're looking for by browsing our active job board or learning more about our operational model.</p><div class=\"space-y-3\"><a href=\"#jobs\" id=\"sidebar-browse-jobs\" class=\"flex items-center justify-between group p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all\"><span class=\"font-bold text-sm tracking-wide\">Browse open jobs</span><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:arrow-right\" class=\"group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"></iconify-icon></a><a href=\"https://p.superdesign.dev/draft/dcbb8baf-c311-42eb-8c3b-01359cbbdafc\" id=\"sidebar-learn-jcl\" class=\"flex items-center justify-between group p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 hover:bg-white/10 transition-all\"><span class=\"font-bold text-sm tracking-wide\">Learn about JCL</span><iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:arrow-right\" class=\"group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform\"></iconify-icon></a></div></div></div></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"bg-[#073057] text-white pt-24 pb-12\" style=\"view-transition-name: footer\"><div class=\"container mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"grid gap-14 lg:grid-cols-12 mb-18\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-8\"><div class=\"flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#1AAD94] shadow-[0_8px_24px_rgba(26,173,148,0.25)]\"><span class=\"text-base font-bold tracking-widest text-white\">JCL</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col leading-tight\"><span class=\"text-lg font-extrabold tracking-tighter uppercase text-white\">JOSEOCEANJOBS</span><span class=\"text-[11px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white/45\">Jose Consulting Limited</span></div></div><p class=\"max-w-md text-[15px] leading-relaxed text-white/65 mb-8\">Jose Consulting Limited helps individuals and organizations strengthen employability, workforce readiness, and global opportunity pathways across the maritime and energy sectors.</p><div class=\"grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm text-white/55\"><div class=\"rounded-[14px] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-4\"><div class=\"text-[#1AAD94] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[10px] mb-2\">Sector focus</div><p>Maritime and energy workforce development</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[14px] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-4\"><div class=\"text-[#1AAD94] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.16em] text-[10px] mb-2\">Mobilization</div><p>Specialist teams deploy within two weeks notice</p></div></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-2\"><h4 class=\"mb-6 text-[13px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#1AAD94]\">Explore</h4><ul class=\"space-y-3 text-white/65\"><li><a href=\"https://p.superdesign.dev/draft/dcbb8baf-c311-42eb-8c3b-01359cbbdafc\" id=\"footer-about\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">About JCL</a></li><li><a href=\"https://p.superdesign.dev/draft/d2d5d0aa-c669-49b6-9b33-a28441cf4b5d\" id=\"footer-leadership\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Leadership & Experts</a></li><li><a href=\"https://p.superdesign.dev/draft/254e9f8f-72d8-4ce3-a2b9-61b026d05b1e\" id=\"footer-partners\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Partnerships & Expertise</a></li><li><a href=\"https://p.superdesign.dev/draft/a44ee394-4e27-4984-95ee-689b5df446b4\" id=\"footer-contact\" class=\"hover:text-[#1AAD94] transition-colors\">Contact JCL</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-2\"><h4 class=\"mb-6 text-[13px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#1AAD94]\">Platform</h4><ul class=\"space-y-3 text-white/65\"><li><a href=\"#jobs\" id=\"footer-jobs\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Browse Jobs</a></li><li><a href=\"#news\" id=\"footer-news\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">News & Insights</a></li><li><a href=\"#directory\" id=\"footer-directory\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Industry Directory</a></li><li><a href=\"#register\" id=\"footer-register\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Start Your Pathway</a></li></ul></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-4\"><h4 class=\"mb-6 text-[13px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#1AAD94]\">How we help</h4><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"rounded-[14px] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5\"><h5 class=\"font-bold text-white mb-1\">Training & consulting enquiries</h5><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/60\">Use the contact flow to discuss workforce development programs, technical training, or operational consulting support.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-[14px] border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5\"><h5 class=\"font-bold text-white mb-1\">Talent pathways</h5><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/60\">Candidates can register, browse opportunities, and connect their skills to future-ready roles.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"pt-10 border-t border-white/10 flex flex-col gap-4 md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between\"><p class=\"text-[12px] font-medium tracking-[0.1em] uppercase text-white/25\">┬